        {
            "title": "美國最高法院一錘定音 川普標志性關稅被推翻",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國最高法院推翻了總統唐納德·川普在全球實施全面關稅的決定，削弱了他標志性的經濟政策，並令他遭受重返白宮以來最大的法律挫敗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">裁決稱，川普動用聯邦緊急權力法在全球範圍內實施「對等」關稅以及政府以應對芬太尼販運加徵針對性進口稅的做法超越了他的權限。大法官們的表決結果為6比3。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大法官們並未就進口商獲得退款的權利程度作出裁決，而是將此留給下級法院處理。倘若全額退款獲得支持，規模可能高達1700億美元，超過川普關稅收入的一半。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cdd1c67d-e643-3b67-969a-f24230e7a54e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持不同意見的大法官Brett Kavanaugh表示，退款流程「可能一片混亂」。另外兩位持異議的大法官是Clarence Thomas和Samuel Alito。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮此前就表示將迅速使用其它法律手段取代關稅，但備選方案往往比川普根據《國際緊急經濟權力法》所動用的廣泛權力更加繁瑣或效果更為有限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump’s Global Tariffs Struck Down by US Supreme Court (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Zoe Tillman.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-%E9%8C%98%E5%AE%9A%E9%9F%B3-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%BF%97%E6%80%A7%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB-152907153.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-21 00:35:14",
