        {
            "title": "歐元區經濟活動上升 得益於德國工業復甦",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"S&amp;amp;P Global\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zfHVbONMne9Kd7XwZ2TLZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/907c76aba403b28cd3e2a2d824444e5f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">S&amp;P Global</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐元區私營部門活動表現超出預期，得益於德國意外成長，製造業創下2022年以來最佳表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">S&amp;P Global編制的綜合採購經理人指數在2月份從前月的51.3升至51.9，持續高於區分經濟擴張與收縮的50臨界點。此前分析師預測該指數將小幅回升至51.5。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P4OJWSQAIkPmNvyhK_9.yA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c103af0d2efd79aaef90c45d8220ce59\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為該地區最大經濟體的德國是主要推動力，隨著政府加大國防和基礎設施支出，製造業在逾三年半以來首次實現擴張。法國數據雖有改善，但仍略低於50的臨界值。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4d17b3d9-c6ea-3e2c-a939-1cb822fcedba-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">漢堡商業銀行經濟學家Cyrus de la Rubia周五在聲明中表示，「現在下結論或許為時尚早，但這可能是製造業的轉折點。」他指出，該行業「已站穩腳跟，今年有望為整體經濟成長作出貢獻，而非拖累經濟成長」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在唐納德·川普關稅攻勢之後，歐洲經濟表現穩健，雖談不上亮眼。今年經濟增速預計略超1%，德國的支出激增將為其提供支撐，而低位穩定的利率已將消費者信心推升至2024年末以來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">S&amp;P Global數據顯示，製造業自2022年以來僅第二次實現成長，而服務業仍保持溫和擴張態勢。但de la Rubia指出，「相較於第四季度，整體成長動能已有所減弱。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行目前無意調整貨幣政策，因其認為通膨率已符合2%的目標，且經濟活力提升需依靠結構性改革而非降低借貸成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Euro-Zone Business Activity Up on German Industrial Revival (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mark Evans、Joel Rinneby、Harumi Ichikura.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
